// ...

// ─── Writer Analytics ───
router.get('/analytics', requireAuth, getWriterAnalyticsController);
```

This requires auth because analytics are personal data. The endpoint is `GET /api/analytics?range=30d`.

---

### 4. Frontend: Client API Function

#### 4A. Addition to `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\API\Api.js`

```javascript
