#### 5E. Chart Components (ViewsChart, ReactionsChart)

Both follow the same pattern -- an `<AreaChart>` from Recharts with the amber accent:

```jsx
import { ResponsiveContainer, AreaChart, Area, XAxis, YAxis, Tooltip, CartesianGrid } from 'recharts';

const ViewsChart = ({ data, range }) => {
    if (!data || data.length === 0) return null;

    // Fill in zero-count days for smooth continuous line
    const filledData = fillMissingDays(data, range);

    return (
        <div className="analytics-chart-card">
            <h3 className="analytics-chart-title">Views</h3>
            <ResponsiveContainer width="100%" height={220}>
