- `var(--border-card)` for card borders
- `var(--shadow-card-sm)` for subtle elevation
- `var(--accent-amber)` for primary accent (chart lines, active range pill)
- `var(--accent-sage)` for secondary accent (publishing frequency bars)
- `var(--text-primary)` for headings
- `var(--text-secondary)` for labels
- `var(--text-muted)` for axis ticks
- `var(--bg-secondary)` for pill inactive state
- `var(--bg-hover)` for hover states
- Font: `'Playfair Display'` for headings, `'Outfit'` for UI elements, `'Lora'` for body/italic

**Key CSS patterns:**

```css
/* ─── Dashboard Container ─── */
.analytics-dashboard {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 0 0 40px;
